t: "Here you are, being invited to donate Ë¹a littleËº in the cause of God. Still some of you withhold. And whoever does so, it is only to their own loss. For God is the Self-Sufficient, whereas you stand in need Ë¹of HimËº. If you Ë¹stillËº turn away, He will replace you with another people. And they will not be like you"